{
  "texts": [
    "• Green: Positive sentiment • Blue: Neutral sentiment • Gray: No sentiment extracted Further, we use color codes for the entity nodes to indicate the role of the entities in concept graphs as follows.",
    "By identifying topics, the NLP analysis allows us to gain an understanding of where the media directed its attention during the energy crisis.",
    "As the topics were given labels separately for each source and sometimes different topics have similar labels (e.g.",
    "'Eurozone economy' and 'European stock market' in The Guardian), it makes sense first to amalgamate some topics manually into broader themes and then try to compare across the different newspapers.",
    "Topics across all newspapers fall into five broad themes: (i) energy and cost of living, (ii) economy, (iii) politics, (iv) geopolitics, and (v) climate change and green energy."
  ]
}